        public DeconvolutionResult(InteractionModelCollection interactionModelCollection,

                           double wholeBloodQTLpvalue)
                    throws java.lang.IllegalAccessException
        Set the deconvolutionResult with the InteractionModels.
        Parameters:
        interactionModelCollection - Collection of the interaction models used to get the deconvolution result
        wholeBloodQTL - Spearman correlation of genotypes and expression levels
        wholeBloodQTLpvalue - pvalue of the pearman correlation of genotypes and expression levels
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalAccessException - QTL name or pvalue can not be retrieved from interactionModelCollection

        celltypes - List of celltypes in the deconvolution result

        pvalues - The pvalues from the deconvolution model

        wholeBloodQTLpvalue - pvalue of the pearman correlation of genotypes and expression levels

      • DeconvolutionResult

        public DeconvolutionResult(java.util.List<java.lang.String> celltypes,
                           java.lang.String qtlName,
                           java.util.List<java.lang.Double> pvalues,
                           double wholeBloodQTL,
                           double wholeBloodQTLpvalue)
        Set the deconvolutionResult without the InteractionModels. This is for when the models are not used, e.g. when option -m is used and not all genotypes have enough samples
        Parameters:
        celltypes - List of celltypes in the deconvolution result
        qtlName - The name of the QTL
        pvalues - The pvalues from the deconvolution model
        wholeBloodQTL - Spearman correlation of genotypes and expression levels
        wholeBloodQTLpvalue - The p-value for whole blood QTL
